c: 4
v: 162
t: "“Koma mwa iwo amene azama pa maphunziro, ndi okhulupirira (onsewo) akukhulupirira zimene zavumbulutsidwa kwa iwe ndi zimene zidavumbulutsidwa patsogolo pako. Ndipo omwe akupitiriza kupemphera Swala, ndi kupereka Zakaati, ndi kukhulupirira Allah komanso tsiku lachimaliziro, iwo tidzawapatsa malipiro aakulu"